{"tid":742551,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"自學物理有冇可能","createTime":"2018-07-14T15:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T12:52:07.000Z","uid":3425,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ef91b5fa1da9539f33d3e6cd77aec8b2387741","tid":742551,"uid":3425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"小弟我由細到大都對唔同既星星，行星，太陽系等天文知識都好有興趣<br />\n但因為細個唔識野，以為讀business就搵到錢<br />\n而走左去讀business, 中學到大學都係讀business<br />\n<br />\n對於天文學，一定要有物理既認識<br />\n但我對於science既知識只有form 3既phy chem bio. <br />\n不過我中學時有學過m2 都叫有小小認識數學既野 不過應該係皮毛<br />\n<br />\n我想問下，如果我想自學物理，可以點入手<br />\n我有諗過由高中既物理自學，我諗自己睇個d教科書應該唔同太難<br />\n<br />\n利申：數底尚算ok，中學讀m2都ok既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb6ff0b14842e0fdeedf1e63639d36dbdf702bf","tid":742551,"uid":20820,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T15:58:31.000Z","msg":"MIT Open Courseware"},{"pid":"9eea839ebf0cb15eb55f88ab1ca134a23958e777","tid":742551,"uid":3220,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T15:58:49.000Z","msg":"中學phy對天文好少關事，都係得circular motion 關關地事，但好多時都唔係circular motion，係橢圓形<br />\n我建議你學識力學果part,再學activation energy ，先再睇其他書會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：dse phy"},{"pid":"35417241baf4586dbdeb043d7f5810401da8a959","tid":742551,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ba139041703fa4bec9e82825adb498e08507097","tid":742551,"uid":12628,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:09:56.000Z","msg":"絕對得，識0-9，a-z 呢幾十個字就搞掂"},{"pid":"af4e2a59687f832e57ce26771d00b70653e12923","tid":742551,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"由dse學起"},{"pid":"03aa9f46700570917c9746c5f162dd1c15c30e61","tid":742551,"uid":41243,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T16:26:15.000Z","m